cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with machine learning models and their vulnerability to adversarial examples. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper proposes a new method for adversarial training using auto-encoders, which involves optimizing the model's architecture and parameters, indicating that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
